Annotations.Annotation: Cube Schema for CCRS - General Profile

ExpressionView.SQL: select b.ISO2 as ISO2, b.NAME as NAME, b.ID as BASE_COUNTRY_ID from BASE_COUNTRY b

SELECT M.ID, AGENCY.LABEL AS AGENCY, COALESCE(REPRESENTATIVE_POST_LEVEL.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as REPRESENTATIVE_POST_LEVEL, COALESCE(AGENCY_REPRESENTATIVE_TITLE.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as AGENCY_REPRESENTATIVE_TITLE, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, COALESCE(COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN M.NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY_COUNT, COALESCE(M.NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY_DIM, CASE WHEN M.has_physical_in_country_presence = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as has_physical_in_country_presence_count, COALESCE(M.has_physical_in_country_presence, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS has_physical_in_country_presence_dim, COALESCE(agency_non_physical_presence.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as agency_non_physical_presence, COALESCE(agency_presence.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as agency_presence FROM CP1UNCTMEMBER M JOIN CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 ON M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID JOIN BASE_COUNTRY bc ON CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 JOIN V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v ON CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR JOIN CATEGORY AGENCY ON M.AGENCY_ID=AGENCY.ID JOIN CATEGORY COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY REPRESENTATIVE_POST_LEVEL ON M.REPRESENTATIVE_POST_LEVEL_ID=REPRESENTATIVE_POST_LEVEL.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY AGENCY_REPRESENTATIVE_TITLE ON M.AGENCY_REPRESENTATIVE_TITLE_ID=AGENCY_REPRESENTATIVE_TITLE.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY agency_non_physical_presence ON M.agency_non_physical_presence_id=agency_non_physical_presence.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY agency_presence ON M.agency_presence_id=agency_presence.ID WHERE CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO'

SELECT M.ID, M.EMAIL, M.NAME, COALESCE(POSITION_TITLE.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as POSITION_TITLE, M.PHONE_NUMBER, AGENCY.LABEL AS AGENCY, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, COALESCE(COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN M.`lead` = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as lead_count, COALESCE(M.`lead`, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS lead_dim FROM CP1UNCGMEMBER M JOIN CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 ON M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID JOIN BASE_COUNTRY bc ON CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 JOIN V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v ON CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR JOIN CATEGORY AGENCY ON M.AGENCY_ID=AGENCY.ID JOIN CATEGORY COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY POSITION_TITLE ON M.POSITION_TITLE_ID=POSITION_TITLE.ID WHERE CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO'

select M.ID, AGENCY.LABEL AS AGENCY, CASE WHEN M.NAME IS NULL THEN '' ELSE M.NAME END as NAME, CASE WHEN M.EMAIL IS NULL THEN '' ELSE M.EMAIL END as EMAIL, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, COALESCE(COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1OMTMEMBER M JOIN CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 ON M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID JOIN BASE_COUNTRY bc ON CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 JOIN V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v ON CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR JOIN CATEGORY AGENCY ON M.AGENCY_ID=AGENCY.ID JOIN CATEGORY COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID WHERE CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO'

select M.ID, M.NAME, COALESCE(RESULTS_GROUP_ALIGNED_TO_SECTOR_GROUPS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as RESULTS_GROUP_ALIGNED_TO_SECTOR_GROUPS, M.OTHER_MEMBER_ORGANIZATIONS, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, COALESCE(COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(M.RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP_DIM, CASE WHEN M.RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP_COUNT, COALESCE(M.JOINT_WORKPLAN, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS JOINT_WORKPLAN_DIM, CASE WHEN M.JOINT_WORKPLAN = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as JOINT_WORKPLAN_COUNT, COALESCE(cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1INTERAGENCY_GROUP M JOIN CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 ON M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID JOIN BASE_COUNTRY bc ON CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 JOIN V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v ON CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR JOIN CATEGORY COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY RESULTS_GROUP_ALIGNED_TO_SECTOR_GROUPS ON M.RESULTS_GROUP_ALIGNED_TO_SECTOR_GROUPS_ID=RESULTS_GROUP_ALIGNED_TO_SECTOR_GROUPS.ID WHERE CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO'

select M.ID, M.COUNTRY_ID as CC_COUNTRY_ID, COALESCE(CC_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as CC_INCOME_STATUS_ID, M.YEAR_OF_BECOMINGDAO as CC_YEAR_OF_BECOMINGDAO, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, COALESCE(COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN M.DAO = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as DAO_COUNT, COALESCE(M.DAO, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS DAO_COUNT_DIM, COALESCE(cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP1COUNTRY M JOIN CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1 ON M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID JOIN BASE_COUNTRY bc ON CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 JOIN V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v ON CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR JOIN CATEGORY COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID LEFT JOIN CATEGORY CC_INCOME_STATUS_ID on M.INCOME_STATUS_ID=CC_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID WHERE CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO'

select CP1.ID, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, COALESCE(COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, COALESCE(resident_coordinator_gender.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as resident_coordinator_gender, COALESCE(CP1.resident_coordinator_nationality_id, -1) AS resident_coordinator_nationality_id, CP1.YEAR_OF_OFFICIAL_REQUEST, COALESCE(PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LDE5.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LDE5, CP1.PROJECTED_TOTALBOSSAVINGS_THIS_YEAR, COALESCE(PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_RESULTS_GROUPS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_RESULTS_GROUPS, COALESCE(PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEB8B.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEB8B, COALESCE(PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK, COALESCE(PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATIO507.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATIO507, COALESCE(cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN cp1.DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP_COUNT, COALESCE(cp1.DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP_DIM, CASE WHEN cp1.COVER_MORE_THAN_ONE_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as COVER_MORE_THAN_ONE_COUNTRY_COUNT, COALESCE(cp1.COVER_MORE_THAN_ONE_COUNTRY, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS COVER_MORE_THAN_ONE_COUNTRY_DIM, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15Q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15Q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10Q_NO, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14Q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15Q_NO, COALESCE(HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN, COALESCE(HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS, COALESCE(HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT, COALESCE(HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS, COALESCE(HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS, COALESCE(HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK, COALESCE(HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK, COALESCE(HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY, COALESCE(HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS, COALESCE(HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES, COALESCE(HASBOSSTRATEGY.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HASBOSSTRATEGY, COALESCE(HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM, COALESCE(HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED, COALESCE(HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY, COALESCE(HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP, COALESCE(GOVERNMENT_ROLE.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as GOVERNMENT_ROLE, COALESCE(SOP1_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SOP1_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS, COALESCE(cp1joint.HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW, CASE cp1joint.HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW WHEN TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW_COUNT, COALESCE(cp1annual.REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV, CASE cp1annual.REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV WHEN TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV_COUNT, COALESCE(SOP2_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SOP2_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS, COALESCE(cp1annual.REPORT_PUBLICLY_AVAILABLE, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS REPORT_PUBLICLY_AVAILABLE_DIM, COALESCE(REPORT_PUBLISHING_MODALITY.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as REPORT_PUBLISHING_MODALITY, COALESCE(cp1jointstrategy.BUDGETED_WORKPLAN, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS BUDGETED_WORKPLAN, CASE cp1jointstrategy.BUDGETED_WORKPLAN WHEN TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as BUDGETED_WORKPLAN_COUNT, COALESCE(cp1jointstrategy.UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT, CASE cp1jointstrategy.UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT WHEN TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT_COUNT, COALESCE(cp1jointstrategy.REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT, 'X-BOOLEAN') AS REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT, CASE cp1jointstrategy.REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT WHEN TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT_COUNT, COALESCE(SOP14_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS.LABEL, 'X-CATEGORY') as SOP14_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS from CP1GENERAL_PROFILE cp1 join CP1JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN cp1joint on cp1joint.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID join CP1ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS cp1annual on cp1annual.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID join CP1JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY cp1jointstrategy on cp1jointstrategy.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID join BASE_COUNTRY bc on CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 join V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v on CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR join CATEGORY COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID left join CATEGORY SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID on CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID=SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN on cp1.HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID=HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS on cp1.HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID=HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT on cp1.HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID=HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS on cp1.HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID=HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS on cp1.HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID=HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK on cp1.HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID=HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK on cp1.HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID=HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY on cp1.HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID=HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS on cp1.HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID=HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES on cp1.HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID=HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES.ID left join CATEGORY HASBOSSTRATEGY on cp1.HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID=HASBOSSTRATEGY.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM on cp1.HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID=HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED on cp1.HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID=HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY on cp1.HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID=HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY.ID left join CATEGORY HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP on cp1.HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID=HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP.ID left join CATEGORY GOVERNMENT_ROLE on cp1joint.GOVERNMENT_ROLE_ID=GOVERNMENT_ROLE.ID left join CATEGORY SOP1_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS on cp1joint.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID=SOP1_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS.ID left join CATEGORY SOP2_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS on cp1annual.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID=SOP2_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS.ID left join CATEGORY PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LDE5 on CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LDE5_ID=PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LDE5.ID left join CATEGORY PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_RESULTS_GROUPS on CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID=PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_RESULTS_GROUPS.ID left join CATEGORY PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEB8B on CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEB8B_ID=PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEB8B.ID left join CATEGORY PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK on CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID=PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK.ID left join CATEGORY PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATIO507 on CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATIO507_ID=PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATIO507.ID left join CATEGORY SOP14_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS on cp1jointstrategy.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID=SOP14_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS.ID left join CATEGORY REPORT_PUBLISHING_MODALITY on cp1annual.REPORT_PUBLISHING_MODALITY_ID=REPORT_PUBLISHING_MODALITY.ID left join CATEGORY resident_coordinator_gender on CP1.resident_coordinator_gender_id=resident_coordinator_gender.ID WHERE
